Git Set Go!

Sri Kadimisetty, Senior

06 Mar 2014

Git is a distributed version control system. It is one skill every software professional is bound to run into in their career. We use it here to run our website and do other cool stuff. You will learn how to manage your projects better with Git be introduced to the popular code sharing website github.com. Participants also get a cool token of appreciation.
